As you know, within the
Kavalan portfolio we have,

00:01:23.230 --> 00:01:25.790
I would say, the most
comprehensive sherry

00:01:25.790 --> 00:01:26.290
portfolio--

00:01:26.290 --> 00:01:26.915
NATE GANA: Yes.

00:01:26.915 --> 00:01:29.220
IAN CHANG: in the
whisky industry.

00:01:29.220 --> 00:01:33.850
Right from Fino Sherry Cask,
Manzanilla, Amontillado,

00:01:33.850 --> 00:01:34.350
and so on.

